WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:04.857
The world of work is undergoing a profound transformation driven by artificial intelligence.

00:00:05.417 --> 00:00:12.186
We are moving into the era of agentic AI, where AI systems act autonomously within multi-step workflows.

00:00:12.746 --> 00:00:15.129
Consider a brief A versus B comparison.

00:00:16.090 --> 00:00:21.414
Option A, a leader spends hours manually assigning tasks to employees.

00:00:22.135 --> 00:00:31.662
Option B, a leader orchestrates a workflow where agentic AI handles routine tasks, allowing employees to focus on complex problem solving.

00:00:32.423 --> 00:00:35.966
Option B represents the future of human AI symbiosis.
